00:53:50,959 --> 00:53:52,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak meminta jawabanmu.</font>

575
00:54:03,570 --> 00:54:04,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

576
00:54:05,769 --> 00:54:06,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu ingin berbicara denganku?</font>

577
00:54:07,709 --> 00:54:08,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

578
00:54:10,479 --> 00:54:13,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kamu pikirkan sampai mempertemukan</font>

579
00:54:13,450 --> 00:54:14,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Ha Jung dengan kakekmu?</font>

580
