00:54:19,419 --> 00:54:21,459
<font color=#FFFF00>mencoba membunuh Seo Won dan Ha Jung.</font>

582
00:54:25,729 --> 00:54:27,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa Ha Jung dalam bahaya.</font>

583
00:54:29,130 --> 00:54:31,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku terpaksa menunjukkan dia kepada Kakek.</font>

584
00:54:53,389 --> 00:54:56,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheong A masih berada di tangan kakekmu.</font>

585
00:54:57,490 --> 00:54:59,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana jika sesuatu terjadi karena tindakanmu malam ini?</font>

586
00:55:05,769 --> 00:55:07,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kehilangan Cheong A,</font>

587
00:55:08,740 --> 00:55:11,369
<font color=#FFFF00>kita bertiga</font>

588
00:55:12,070 --> 00:55:13,680
<font color=#FFFF00>akan mati.</font>

589
00:55:17,410 --> 00:55:18,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

590
00:55:19,410 --> 00:55:20,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa pun perkataan ibu,</font>

591
00:55:23,249 --> 00:55:25,519
<font color=#FFFF00>sekeras apa pun Pil Joo mencoba menghentikanku,</font>

592
00:55:25,990 --> 00:55:27,059
<font color=#FFFF00>aku akan</font>

593
00:55:28,320 --> 00:55:31,389
<font color=#FFFF00>menjadikan Ha Jung anakku!</font>

594
00:55:33,260 --> 00:55:34,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa pun yang terjadi,</font>

595
00:55:35,729 --> 00:55:37,900
<font color=#FFFF00>aku akan melindungi Ha Jung.</font>

596
00:56:07,130 --> 00:56:08,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Boo Cheon.</font>

597
00:56:17,570 --> 00:56:19,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mau masalah kita selesai.</font>

598
00:56:22,740 --> 00:56:25,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu kita tidak akan pernah sama seperti sebelumnya.</font>

599
00:56:26,849 --> 00:56:29,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi sebelum membawa Ha Jung kepada Kakek,</font>

600
00:56:30,849 --> 00:56:33,389
<font color=#FFFF00>kamu seharusnya memberitahuku.</font>

601
00:56:33,990 --> 00:56:34,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

602
00:56:35,860 --> 00:56:37,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memiliki alasan.</font>

603
00:56:37,160 --> 00:56:38,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Mulai sekarang,</font>

604
00:56:40,360 --> 00:56:42,499
<font color=#FFFF00>tolong pertimbangkan perasaanku.</font>

605
00:56:44,729 --> 00:56:47,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku selalu terlambat mengetahui, lalu akhirnya terkejut dan terluka.</font>

606
00:56:52,669 --> 00:56:53,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sulit.</font>

607
00:56:54,780 --> 00:56:56,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memiliki alasan...</font>

608
00:57:02,950 --> 00:57:04,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku, Mo Hyun.</font>

609
00:57:54,070 --> 00:57:55,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah Pil Joo sukses,</font>

610
00:57:55,939 --> 00:57:57,740
<font color=#FFFF00>ada banyak sekali rumor.</font>

611
00:57:58,309 --> 00:58:00,639
<font color=#FFFF00>"Pil Joo yang asli sudah mati."</font>

612
00:58:03,180 --> 00:58:05,380
<font color=#FFFF00>"Anak yang dibawa wanita itu dari Seoul</font>

613
00:58:05,650 --> 00:58:08,019
<font color=#FFFF00>hidup menggantikan anak yang sudah mati</font>

614
00:58:08,650 --> 00:58:10,150
<font color=#FFFF00>dan menjadi pengacara."</font>

615
00:58:12,650 --> 00:58:14,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada banyak rumor semacam itu.</font>

616
00:58:18,660 --> 00:58:23,030
<font color=#FFFF00>"Eksekutif Jung Mal Ran"</font>

617
00:58:33,880 --> 00:58:35,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Selama 30 tahun terakhir,</font>

618
00:58:37,150 --> 00:58:39,749
<font color=#FFFF00>aku mengalami mimpi buruk yang mengerikan ini.</font>

619
00:58:41,820 --> 00:58:43,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Kecuali aku mati</font>

620
00:58:44,150 --> 00:58:45,749
