648
01:01:59,680 --> 01:02:00,780
<font color=#FFFF00>"Kang Pil Joo"</font>

649
01:02:34,019 --> 01:02:35,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekretaris Oh.</font>

650
01:02:43,119 --> 01:02:44,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Sedang apa kamu di sini?</font>

651
01:02:45,630 --> 01:02:46,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengacara Kang.</font>

652
01:02:48,930 --> 01:02:49,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana?</font>

653
01:02:50,630 --> 01:02:51,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu menemukan Jang Eun Cheon?</font>

654
01:02:55,869 --> 01:02:57,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Eksekutif Jung.</font>

655
01:02:59,910 --> 01:03:01,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Jang Eun Cheon adalah...</font>

656
01:03:19,889 --> 01:03:22,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah kamu Jang Eun Cheon?</font>

657
01:03:24,070 --> 01:03:25,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

658
01:03:26,269 --> 01:03:27,499
<font color=#FFFF00>Baguslah.</font>

659
01:03:29,599 --> 01:03:31,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan ponselnya.</font>

660
01:03:33,639 --> 01:03:35,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Eksekutif Jung</font>

661
01:03:36,380 --> 01:03:39,249
<font color=#FFFF00>akan bahagia saat mengetahui aku menemukan Jang Eun Cheon.</font>

662
01:03:41,450 --> 01:03:42,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Eksekutif Jung berjanji</font>

663
01:03:43,419 --> 01:03:45,289
<font color=#FFFF00>akan menjadikanmu saudara Direktur Jang</font>

664
01:03:46,450 --> 01:03:48,160
<font color=#FFFF00>agar dia tidak kesepian.</font>

665
01:03:52,360 --> 01:03:55,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kamu merahasiakan dirimu dengan mengatakan</font>

666
01:03:55,630 --> 01:03:57,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Cha Tae Young adalah Jang Eun Cheon?</font>

667
01:03:58,200 --> 01:03:59,669
