01:05:06,499 --> 01:05:09,840
<font color=#FFFF00>memberi tahu siapa pun bahwa aku Jang Eun Cheon.</font>

689
01:05:19,849 --> 01:05:21,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa menurutmu begitu?</font>

690
01:05:25,349 --> 01:05:26,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena</font>

